statements: SELECT * FROM session_log;
SELECT session_id, start_time, end_time, duration FROM session_log ORDER BY start_time DESC;
SELECT * FROM session_log WHERE duration > '1 hour';

SELECT * FROM session_log WHERE end_time < '2022-01-01' AND duration > INTERVAL '1 hour' ORDER BY end_time ASC;
SELECT session_id, start_time, end_time, duration FROM session_log WHERE duration > INTERVAL '30 minutes' AND start_time BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-12-31' ORDER BY duration DESC;
SELECT session_id, start_time, end_time, duration FROM session_log WHERE end_time < '2022-06-01' AND duration < INTERVAL '2 hours' ORDER BY session_id ASC;
SELECT session_id, start_time, end_time, EXTRACT(day FROM duration) AS duration_days FROM session_log WHERE EXTRACT(day FROM duration) >= 1 ORDER BY duration_days DESC;
